ing team though it would be another 26 years before the death of the Francisco Varallolast surviving participant of that World Cuprefhttpwwwbbccouknewsworldlatinamerica11134965 Last surviving player from first World Cup final dies BBC News 31 Aug 2010 22 March 2011ref